name: my 1/2 finished game for the autumn game jam
name_original: my 1/2 finished game for the autumn game jam
description:
A prototype that has procedural generation and is a 1/2 finished game.

Please tell me if it would be cool if I went all out on this game.

WASD to move, press f to chop down trees. I need to add a day/night cycle and enemies. Currently, there is only procedural generation and chopping down trees.
